{"tid":970264,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[宅男隨意走] 東壩半日遊","createTime":"2019-01-05T16:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T05:42:09.000Z","uid":141044,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1a9b8ad5bc7700e75e2d35be5961845c8a4fc088","tid":970264,"uid":141044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T16:21:37.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟最期六去左西貢火山探知館既東壩半日遊，覺得幾正，想同巴打們分享下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有三班車，我搭左最早既一班車 （九點半上車，十二點半回程）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K64RJ32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK64RJ32.jpg&h=92921cd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n火山探知館出面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/edWAriB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FedWAriB.jpg&h=a56b3732&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天氣麻麻，能見度低 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tjSLOwX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtjSLOwX.jpg&h=78d62d68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為太早，所以我嗰班車得六個團友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n架車喺附近運動場上<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/60drxYD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F60drxYD.jpg&h=1a7114e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沿途會經西壩 （下面幅圖可能唔關事）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3kPRJ7i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3kPRJ7i.jpg&h=7bf60f41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n牛出沒注意<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EwifrkY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEwifrkY.jpg&h=3c5aff4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一落車就見到另一隻牛<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bn1XEGa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbn1XEGa.jpg&h=5fc86db7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來有小巴線去到東壩，但係紅日下晝先有<br />\n呢條小巴線開左唔夠半年<br />\n<br />\n落車行前兩步會見到呢舊藍色弱波石，紀念因為水壩工程而喪生既人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4hhctAr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4hhctAr.jpg&h=8c6238c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8c8abf57a970cbd1ff9a4cbaff6df180b502821","tid":970264,"uid":141044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T16:27:43.000Z","msg":"東壩有個資訊亭俾人問野同攞地圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6VsWVg6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6VsWVg6.jpg&h=623e884d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上得一條路行，所以唔攞地圖都ok<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ut3ZS4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fut3ZS4t.jpg&h=b17d2d49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/viXPvQv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FviXPvQv.jpg&h=78fd55b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UZ3yXwT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUZ3yXwT.jpg&h=cc765d61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UCqxtDz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUCqxtDz.jpg&h=4c1368d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TYjRKbW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTYjRKbW.jpg&h=4c9d82e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07ti8DC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07ti8DC.jpg&h=d7ff5ce4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33999b73fc4fc31886494126cb1aabfacb873242","tid":970264,"uid":141044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T16:35:32.000Z","msg":"沿住一開始條路向前行，會見到一個太陽能洗手間<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OeX0CxE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOeX0CxE.jpg&h=1cd9e89b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pVpeGZk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpVpeGZk.jpg&h=05ec3f63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o3rXEL2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo3rXEL2.jpg&h=b895451b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個洗手間比我想像中乾淨（呢個我冇影，大家發揮下你既想像力啦）<br />\n<br />\n去完洗手間之後向住海嗰邊行<br />\n東壩d岩石好正<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/smeeG0y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsmeeG0y.jpg&h=fa55efb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家去既話要小心<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tyL5OFE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtyL5OFE.jpg&h=540c09ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nCVNhzi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnCVNhzi.jpg&h=2ddee84e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MgoOMsw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMgoOMsw.jpg&h=cbf41aad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee3b9f766864dd5ee197eb381c64434518eb6937","tid":970264,"uid":141044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T16:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OUzyc83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOUzyc83.jpg&h=b95fff79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多弱波石<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sDtbKfL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsDtbKfL.jpg&h=a6619fd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z18yXAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz18yXAM.jpg&h=f1f1c3e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9scTc88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9scTc88.jpg&h=39ba9a49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G0k9vVP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG0k9vVP.jpg&h=d36d87bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E742QVQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE742QVQ.jpg&h=43951f47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24d7d52c8e563ead0531977fd06ed51a50f601ab","tid":970264,"uid":59804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T16:44:55.000Z","msg":"點解會去？"},{"pid":"a8142aa659daef2ab8ef782654ad008a4d6182aa","tid":970264,"uid":141044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24d7d52c8e563ead0531977fd06ed51a50f601ab","tid":970264,"uid":59804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T16:44:55.000Z","msg":"點解會去？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:23:42.000Z","msg":"岩岩走左班巴士，巴士站附近見到一張關於東壩既宣傳poster"},{"pid":"c53a383ca40bfd520ae6e211ab7de2df2663d382","tid":970264,"uid":141044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:28:17.000Z","msg":"有d人喺弱波石上面塗鴉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LAu6FKD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLAu6FKD.jpg&h=406bcbbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Gify4u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Gify4u.jpg&h=9d64d333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TBJy5bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTBJy5bb.jpg&h=8772a0c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCyfy4x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCyfy4x.jpg&h=3c83c622&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9ugkLbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ugkLbe.jpg&h=b6c2b493&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jp52d4A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJp52d4A.jpg&h=ceaea158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xq8Z0KC.jpg\" d